The thought for this project is have a robot that will be able to respond to voice commands. This project goes hand and hand with 
the file for gesture driven robot, but they are seperate for clarity sake. 
The goal for this project is to help elderly, or incapacitated individuals who need help for doing simple tasks. A few being, taking 
garbage out, starting dish washer, turning off lights, keep track of appointments, etc. 

BUILD:
1) Microphone to pick user voice.
2) Microcontroller that can be programmed with tasks.
3) Robotic arm to pick up and perform tasks. 
4) Ability to avoid obstacles and read the room. 
